column1: #Text=Well , Molossian culture is a mix of several sources .
#Text=Above all , we value the lifestyle of the western U.S. , especially as it pertains to living in a wide-open place such as we do .
#Text=Life here is fairly relaxed and easygoing , and we do most things together as a nation and as a family .
#Text=In addition , we have absorbed elements of other cultures .
#Text=The town of Steinsdorf on the Molossia Railroad is , of course , German .
#Text=Our National Hero , Emperor Norton , comes from San Francisco .
#Text=Cookie Dough , our National Treat , is adopted from the United Provinces of Utopia , a micronation with whom we once associated .
#Text=How are Molossia 's relations with other micronations ?
#Text=We maintain friendly , informal relations with just about every micronation .
#Text=Our hand is always outstretched in friendship .
#Text=With some nations we are particularly close , such as with TorHavn and Vikesland , due to the long and positive relationship that we have had .
#Text=We count ourselves lucky to have good friends among many other micronations and micronationalists , from all over the world .
#Text=The land claimed by Molossia is also claimed by the United States .
#Text=How are relations between your country and the U.S. ?
#Text=Or do you generally leave each other alone ?
#Text=No , there have n't been any altercations between Molossia and the US .
#Text=We ca n't really live without the US , though , since they provide a significant amount of our consumer goods , Molossia being rather resource-poor .
#Text=And as long as we do n't do anything objectionable , they leave us alone .
#Text=Besides the League of Small Nations , a nearly defunct association devoted to the prosperity of all land-claiming micronations , does Molossia belong to any international organizations ?
#Text=Actually , no we do n't , although we certainly have over the years , especially league of Secessionist States ( LoSS ) , although we withdrew from that organization years ago .
#Text=Incidentally , the League of Small nations is in the process of being resurrected , with an eye toward increased intermicronational activities , to possibly include supporting a charity .
#Text=Can one become a citizen of Molossia ?
#Text=Well , Molossian citizenship is only extended to actual , physical residents of Molossia , and we are not accepting any immigrants at this time .
#Text=Honorary citizenship is indeed granted , generally to those individuals that have performed some special service to Molossia , and have thus earned our gratitude .
#Text=Yes , all Molossians are dual US citizens .
#Text=Most Molossians actually work in the US and live in Molossia , largely due to our small size and lack of resources .
#Text=And no , as a sovereign nation , we do not pay taxes to the US .
#Text=However , we contribute an equivalent amount to the US in Foreign Aid , in the hopes that they will someday fix their roads !
